{"tid":231530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【爭公義15年】少女遭35暴徒輪姦 醒來14名家人全死包括B女","createTime":"2017-05-06T06:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T12:08:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"613a500505f499b8aa765f6454855282d6344c04","tid":231530,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170505/large/1493977958_6006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170505%2Flarge%2F1493977958_6006.jpg&h=b77e2b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170506&amp;guid=56654360&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170506%26guid%3D56654360%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=07c54162\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170506%26guid%3D56654360%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=bc0f9cc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170506&amp;guid=56654360&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n即時國際  2017-05-06 00:04:15 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n印度一名女子在19歲時遭暴徒輪姦至不省人事，醒來後發現自己14名家人被殺，她這15年來一直尋求公義，當地最高法院周四終於還她一個公道，維持11名被告終身監禁，同時取消其餘7名被告早前獲無罪釋放的判決。<br />\n<br />\n巴諾（Bilkis Bano）與家人住在古吉拉特邦（Gujarat），2002年她懷孕5個月時，當地爆發暴動，她帶同2歲女兒與家人乘坐一架卡車離家避難，卻被35名暴徒襲擊，她的女兒頭部被人打至不似人形，她自己亦被輪姦，之後被遺棄在那裡等死。<br />\n<br />\n不過，巴諾卻活過來了，三小時後她醒來，發現自己全身赤裸。「我全身赤裸，我見到四周躺着家人的屍體，我很害怕，我周圍找衣服遮掩身體，我被神拯救了。」她後來在山上一個部落家族尋求庇護，雖然她是文盲又沒有錢，但仍然決定走去警局報案。<br />\n<br />\n豈料這才是噩夢的開始，警員不肯受理她的案件，更威脅如果她報案的話，醫院便會向她注射毒針殺死她。一年後她入稟當地法院，但法院稱她的口供有矛盾而結案。巴諾沒有放棄，找上國家人權委員會，甚至請求最高法院介入，終於迫使印度中央調查局（CBI）立案展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n巴諾仍苦等了4年，案件才由家鄉移至孟買審訊，政府終於派出檢察官起訴20人，包括警員及政府醫生。2008年1月，11名男子因強暴及謀殺而被判終身監禁，另外兩人亦罪成，但有7人脫罪。在事發後15年，巴諾終於獲得遲來的公義，最高法院周四裁定，之前被判無罪的7名醫生及警員，則因為篡改證據而被定罪。"},{"pid":"3ae3278731789e67fad0886c374278a732f30bbe","tid":231530,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb606cf68620e39af42c073488c90e560b178854","tid":231530,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddac8750cade155536ede460b0901f878fdb00c","tid":231530,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼最後惡人有惡報，响支那條女死左十世"},{"pid":"67f4a13dc5b4d6a7c987c62c0ae1b5356ede9961","tid":231530,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"常威做既？"},{"pid":"992d17dfb264f12156f360de3b00c69f52715482","tid":231530,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>常威做既？</blockquote><br />\n印度常威"},{"pid":"947994ef1227eca6e047525ee977ce5f5a077cb6","tid":231530,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"戚秦氏"},{"pid":"e0d963ae7d0b2be004ab09ce5180d55c52d45a5d","tid":231530,"uid":61920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"我彈出彈入"},{"pid":"840b009c38ba35319b07a4af4d26fd3cdcc77e06","tid":231530,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33baa01feeb60e2633866144ed9a4f1638accbc8","tid":231530,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo