是人就更加唔明。<br />\n<br />\n係咪只因為做唔到棄舊立新？定又係百搭貪污問題？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宗教，種姓問題<br />\n剩係種姓呢樣野，已經好難搞<br />\n佢地黎一次文革，或者可以搞得掂<br />\n分左幾個階級既姓氏<br />\n婆羅門(祭司與教師)、剎帝利(士兵和統治者)、吠舍(普通勞動者、商人、農人、工匠)和首陀羅(奴隸)，至於賤民被種姓制度排除在外。自命高人一等，天之驕子，強姦你係益你咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6b2c8d5f77c60e599660a613d5b7a6af7cce2c","tid":231530,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>常威做既？</blockquote><br />\n印度常威</blockquote><br />\n戚家十三口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係即時諗起戚秦氏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}